          <title>Salah scores and Liverpool still perfect in Champions League with 1-0 win over Girona</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Mohamed Salah scored a second-half penalty to maintain Liverpool's perfect Champions League record in a 1-0 win over Girona on Tuesday. A sixth straight win kept the Merseyside club at the top of the revamped 36-team league stage — five points clear of second place Inter Milan.]]></description>
